node.title: Pair killed in Kaeo highway crash named
node.description: Police have released the names of two people who died in a crash near Kaeo on State Highway 10 on Saturday.
node.content:
["Police have released the names of two people who died in a crash near Kaeo in the Far North on State Highway 10 on Saturday.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Denise Samson, 47, and Shannon Herbert, 11, both from Kerikeri, died in the two-vehicle crash south of Kaeo Bridge just after midday on 2 April.", "Four other people were seriously injured and remain stable in hospital.", "Police said an investigation into the crash was ongoing and extended sincere condolences to family and friends."]
